scopecontent.p:
This series contains issues of several literary journals produced by Packer students and faculty. Specific titles include 
                        School-Room Echoes, 1852 to 1853; 
                        The Neophite, 1860 to 1861; 
                        The Phoenix, 1867; 
                        The Packer Quarterly, 1869 to 1875; 
                        The Packer '90, 1890; 
                        Packer Current Items, 1925 to 1970; and 
                        The Packer PEN, 1964 to 1970.
